  m_Name: D4FMD
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - You got the info from the website ready?
  - "You: Oh, yes. I wrote down what I found on it. I\u2019ll send over a scan"
  - "\u2026"
  - "All those outsiders falling for their bullshit just as much as everyone here\u2026.
    had they had even an ounce of ability to see through someone maybe we would\u2019ve
    had some real help by now."
  - "But the majority of it isn\u2019t surprising\u2026 just more fucking lies and
    deception on every front."
  - "\u2026.. Good work, either way. I\u2019ve got some more info to share."
  - Confirms all those rumours I was going on about yesterday, probably links with
    the spy investigation aswell.
  - "Speaking of, he wants a word with you today. You\u2019ll see him at some point,
    name will be like Ivan or something? pretty tall guy, and he\u2019ll be all friendly,
    talkative, generic nobody kind of attitude everyone you\u2019ll encounter has."
  - "Codeword FACTION and he\u2019ll drop the act give you the real him."
  - 'You: Alright, thanks'
  - "\u2026."
  - "\u2026. Say"
  - "\u2026. We were, in the same class at school, right? You were that friendless
    kid, like 3rd or 4th row."
  - "You: Huh? Oh, yeah. I was thinking of the same, weren\u2019t you the one at
    the far back, that would always push everyone away?"
  - "Well\u2026 maybe if one of those dumb fucking teachers actually tried helping
    me I wouldn\u2019t have had to."
  - "You: Why didn\u2019t you talk to them about it?"
  - "Why didn\u2019t THEY talk to ME about it? They were perfectly fine helping everyone
    else weren\u2019t they?"
  - "Whatever, just look out for the spy. This\u2019ll be through soon enough, and
    I can finally show the world how disgusting this government really is."
  bridgeAfterDialogue: 0
  clearTranscriptUponBridging: 0
